d. I also expect to receive shortly a legal opinion direct from Paris which it might be interesting to compare to the one you may obtain.





Sincerely yours,

Vladimir Nabokov





TO: WALTER J. MINTON

CC, 1 p.





Goldwin Smith Hall

Cornell University

Ithaca, N.Y.

November 29, 1957

Dear Mr. Minton,

It was nice of you to telephone. I would like to repeat that, although McDowell, Obolensky did make an offer for LOLITA, no agreement has been signed, nor am I under any definite commitment,